    gatekeeping: "Moderate \u2014 respect for tradition expected. Debates about purity vs. evolution. Cultural ownership discussions. Live playing ability is the ultimate gatekeeper.",
    livePerformance: "The blues is a live music form \u2014 clubs, juke joints, and festivals. Intimate venues where artist and audience connect directly. Extended solos and improvisation. Audience call-and-response.",
