    adlibStyle: 'Essential \u2014 "Thank you Jesus!", "Hallelujah!", "Yes Lord!", "Glory!", "Have mercy!", "Come on!", "Somebody praise Him!" Ad-libs intensify through the song toward the praise break.',
    harmony: "Rich choir harmonies \u2014 4-part SATB standard. Unison singing for power. Divisi (splitting into more parts) for climactic moments. Call-and-response between lead and choir. Background humming and sustained tones.",
    grit: "Natural and intense \u2014 grit comes from emotional/spiritual intensity. The voice breaking with emotion is celebrated, not avoided. Raw vocal power over polished perfection."
