    regionWithinCulture: "Rio de Janeiro owns samba, bossa nova, and funk carioca. Bahia owns ax\xE9 and samba de roda. Pernambuco owns frevo and maracatu. The Northeast owns forr\xF3 and bai\xE3o. S\xE3o Paulo and the interior own sertanejo. Each region defends its genres with fierce pride."
