    weightAndMomentum: "Bongo Flava carries warm weight through sub-bass and round synth tones. Benga is lighter and more nimble \u2014 the clean guitar tones create buoyancy. Singeli is weightless and chaotic \u2014 speed replaces gravity. Taarab has the weight of ceremony and tradition.",
    urgencyScale: "Taarab creates emotional urgency through vocal intensity, not tempo. Bongo Flava creates groove urgency \u2014 the need to move the body. Singeli is maximum physical urgency \u2014 the tempo demands response. Benga creates joyful urgency through guitar interplay.",
